ine-height: 24px">Industri plastik (membuat mould, pisau giling, granulator, spare part untuk mould dan mesin injector).</span></span></li>\r\n	<li class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; list-style-image: url(&#39;http://disperindag.jatimprov.go.id/themes/higherground/images/bullet.gif&#39;); line-height: 16px"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: xx-small"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px">Industri otomotif ( membuat tools, &amp; dies untuk knalpot, velg alumunium, measuring instrument, dll).</span></span></li>\r\n	<li class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; list-style-image: url(&#39;http://disperindag.jatimprov.go.id/themes/higherground/images/bullet.gif&#39;); line-height: 16px"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: xx-small"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px">Industri playwood/kayu.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; list-style-image: url(&#39;http://disperindag.jatimprov.go.id/themes/higherground/images/bullet.gif&#39;); line-height: 16px"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: xx-small"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px">Industri packging (printing equipment, roll printing, pisau slitter, dll).</span></span></li>\r\n	<li class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; list-style-image: url(&#39;http://disperindag.jatimprov.go.id/themes/higherground/images/bullet.gif&#39;); line-height: 16px"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: xx-small"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px">Industri korek api (membuat spare part untuk mesin-mesinnya).</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n', '2012-11-19', '');
