endirian Perusahaan</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px none; list-style-image: url(&#39;&quot;../themes/higherground/images/bullet.gif&quot;&#39;)">N P W P</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px none; list-style-image: url(&#39;&quot;../themes/higherground/images/bullet.gif&quot;&#39;)">Sketsa Rencana Lokasi</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px none; list-style-image: url(&#39;&quot;../themes/higherground/images/bullet.gif&quot;&#39;)">Surat\r\n	pernyataan dari perusahaan yang bersangkutan bahwa rencana lokasi \r\n	terletak dalam kawasan peruntukan industri sesuai dengan RUTR / RDTR dan\r\n	tidak terletak pada lahan yang beririgasi teknis</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px; outline: 0px none; color: #666666; font-family: Verdana,Tahoma,arial,sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 16.7833px">\r\n<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px none">2. Izin Usaha Kawasan Industri (IUKI)</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<ul class="unIndentedList" style="margin: 5px 20px; padding: 0px 20px; outline: 0px none; list-style: none outside none; color: #666666; font-family: Verdana,Tahoma,arial,sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 16.7833px">\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px none; list-style-image: url(&#39;&quot;../themes/higherground/images/bullet.gif&quot;&#39;)">Mengisi formulir Model PMK III</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px none; list-style-image: url(&#39;&quot;../themes/higherground/images/bullet.gif&quot;&#39;)">Melampirkan Formulir Model PMK - III (informasi pembangunan proyek)</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px none; list-style-image: url(&#39;&quot;../themes/higherground/images/bullet.gif&quot;&#39;)">Susunan Direksi dan Komisaris Perusahaan</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px none; list-style-image: url(&#39;&quot;../themes/higherground/images/bullet.gif&quot;&#39;)">Izin - izin l