sp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: &#39;Century Gothic&#39;,sans-serif">Universal Belt\r\nSander&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="white-space: pre" class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>- Holloe\r\nChiesel</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt" class="MsoNormal">\r\n<!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: &#39;Century Gothic&#39;,sans-serif">-<span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: &#39;Century Gothic&#39;,sans-serif">Knife\r\nGrinder&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;-\r\nPresision Band Saw</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt" class="MsoNormal">\r\n<!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: &#39;Century Gothic&#39;,sans-serif">-<span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: &#39;Century Gothic&#39;,sans-serif">Circular Saw&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- Dan mesin\r\nmesin industri</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt" class="MsoNormal">\r\n<!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: &#39;Century Gothic&#39;,sans-serif">-<span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font